lead_paragraph: Michael Phelps is dropping the 200-meter freestyle at the U.S. swimming trials, leaving the 18-time Olympic gold medalist with four events.

headline.main: Phelps Drops 200 Free at Olympic Trials; Will Swim 4 Events
